Title: The King's Man
Writer: Karl Gajdusek (screenplay), Dave Gibbons (characters), Jane Goldman (screenplay), Mark Millar (characters), Matthew Vaughn (characters), Matthew Vaughn (screenplay)
Actors: Gemma Arterton, Aaron Taylor-Johnson, Matthew Goode, Ralph Fiennes
Plot: As a collection of history's worst tyrants and criminal masterminds gather to plot a war to wipe out millions, one man must race against time to stop them.
